erecha\">\n                <h2>DESCUBRE TODOS LOS DETALLES DEL GRAN CIRCO</h2>\n                <p>En <strong>Mundo F1</strong>, podrás encontrar toda la información, estadísticas y últimas noticias relacionadas con la máxima categoría de los deportes de motor. Aquí dispondrás de la información actualizada tras cada <strong>Gran Premio</strong> con todos los datos actualizados al minuto, sesión a sesión.</p>\n                <p>Explora nuestro sitio y descubre una nueva manera de disfrutar de tu <strong>deporte favorito</strong>.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>    \n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"contenedor-tarjetas-columnas\">\n        <div class=\"tarjeta-estilo\">\n          <div class=\"tarjeta-imagen\">\n            <img src=\"https://cdn.avpasion.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sigue-gp-bahrein-formula-1-web-02.jpg\" alt=\"live-timing\" class=\"foto-tarjeta\"/>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"tarjeta-contenido\">\n            <h3>Live Timings</h3>\n            <p>No hay sesiones en directo.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"tarjeta-boton\">Ver más</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"tarjeta-estilo\">\n          <div class=\"tarjeta-imagen\">\n            <img src=\"https://media.revistagq.com/photos/67e3e76c647fcc7e2803ca27/16:9/w_2560%2Cc_limit/2187699741\" alt=\"tsunoda-lawson\" class=\"foto-tarjeta\"/>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"tarjeta-contenido\">\n            <h3>Últimas noticias</h3>\n            <p>Yuki Tsunoda, a Red Bull: Liam Lawson pilotará el RB a partir de Suzuka.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"tarjeta-boton\">Ver más</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"tarjeta-estilo\">\n          <div class=\"tarjeta-imagen\">\n            <img src=\"https://s10.s3c.es/imag/_v0/5120x2794/b/8/3/BBPHDB.jpg\" alt=\"Japon\" class=\"foto-tarjeta\"/>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"tarjeta-contenido\">\n            <h3>Próxima Carrera</h3>\n            <p>Toda la información sobre el GP de Japón.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"tarjeta-boton\">Ver más</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"tarjeta-estilo\">\n            <div class=\"tarjeta-imagen\">\n              <img src=\"https://imgresizer.eurosport.com/unsafe/1200x0/filters:format(jpeg)/origin-imgresizer.eurosport.com/2025/02/28/image-90710e0d-1722-4256-9cad-488a339e1c9b-85-2560-1440.jpeg\" alt=\"sainz-alonso\" class=\"foto-tarjeta\"/>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"tarjeta-contenido\">\n              <h3>Españoles</h3>\n              <p>Últimas noticias sobre Fernando Alonso y Carlos Sainz.</p>\n              <a href=\"#\" class=\"tarjeta-boton\">Ver más</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"pie-de-pagina\">\n        <div class=\"container-redes-sociales\">\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"redes-sociales\">Instagram</a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"redes-sociales\">Facebook</a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"redes-sociales\">X</a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"redes-sociales\">Tik Tok</a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"redes-sociales\">Contacto</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"texto-pie\">\n            <p>Esta página ha sido realizada por Pedro de la Rúa Lima.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n</body>\n</html>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->3', 'Max Verstappen', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '65-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-04-03 11:45:28', '2025-04-03 09:45:28', '', 65, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=67', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(68, 2, '2025-04-03 11:50:08', '2025-04-03 09:50:08', '<!-- wp:html -->\n<style>\n.body {\n    width: 100vw !important;\n    max-width: 100% !important;\n    margin: 0 !important;\n    padding: 0 !important;\n}\n\n.barra-superior,\n.cuerpo,\n.contenedor-imagen-texto,\n.contenedor-tarjetas-columnas,\n.pie-de-pagina {\n    width: 100% !important;\n    max-width: 100% !important;\n    margin-left: 0 !important;\n    margin-right: 0 !important;\n    padding-left: 0 !important;\n    padding-right: 0 !important;\n}\n\n.encabezado-superior {\n    width: 60% !important;\n}\n\n    :root {\n    --color-primario: #ff0000;\n    --color-secundario: #292929;\n    --color-terciario: #ffffff;\n    --color-texto: #ffffff;\n    --color-texto-alt: #292929;\n}\n\nbody {\n    margin: 0;\n    font-family: \'Exo 2\';\n    background-image: url(\'https://png.pngtree.com/png-clipart/20240812/original/pngtree-pattern-lines-seamless-vector-png-image_15752243.png\');\n    background-position: center;\n    background-size: cover;\n    background-attachment: fixed;\n}\n\n.barra-superior {\n    position:;\n    top: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    max-width: 100vw;\n    padding: 10px 20px;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    justify-items: center;\n    z-index: 1000;\n    margin: 0;\n}\n\n.encabezado-superior {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    border-radius: 30px;\n    width: 55%;\n    padding: 4px;\n    background-color: var(--color-primario);\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    position: relative;\n    box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n}\n\n.botones-izquierda {\n    display: flex;\n    font-size: 25px;\n    gap: 10px;\n    flex: 1;\n    justify-content: right;\n}\n\n.botones-derecha {\n    display: flex;\n    font-size: 25px;\n    gap: 10px;\n    flex: 1;\n    justify-content: left;\n}\n\n.boton-header {\n    padding: 10px 20px;\n    color: var(--color-texto);\n    text-decoration: none;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    border-radius: 15px;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n    display: inline-block;\n    background: none;\n    border: none;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    font-family: inherit;\n    font-size: inherit;\n}\n\n.boton-header:hover {\n    background-color: var(--color-texto);\n    color: var(--color-texto-alt);\n}\n\n.icono-boton img {\n    height: 100px;\n    width: auto;\n    transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.icono-boton:hover img {\n    transform: scale(1.1);\n}\n\n.menu-desplegable {\n    position: relative;\n    display: inline-block;\n}\n\n.contenido-menus {\n    display: none;\n    position: absolute;\n    background-color: var(--color-terciario);\n    width: 100%;\n    min-width: max-content;\n    box-shadow: 0px 8px 16px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n    z-index: 1;\n    border-radius: 0 0 15px 15px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    top: 100%;\n    left: 0;\n}\n\n.contenido-menus a {\n    color: var(--color-texto-alt);\n    padding: 12px 16px;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    display: block;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    transition: background-color 0.3s;\n}\n\n.contenido-menus a:hover {\n    background-color: #f1f1f1;\n}\n\n.menu-desplegable:hover .contenido-menus {\n    display: block;\n}\n\n.menu-desplegable > .boton-header {\n    width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    text-align: center;\n}\n\n.menu-desplegable:hover .boton-header {\n    background-color: var(--color-texto);\n    color: var(--color-primario);\n    border-radius: 15px 15px 0 0;\n}\n\n.cuerpo {\n    margin-top: 50px;\n    height: 40vh;\n    background-image: url(\'https://www.formula1.com/content/dam/fom-website/manual/Misc/2022manual/WinterFebruary/GettyImages-1235524583.jpg\');\n    background-position-x: center;\n    background-position-y: -60vh;\n    background-size: cover;\n    height: 300px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    position: relative;\n    box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n}\n\n.cuerpo::befo