/media/press/0001/16/ca89fcd285389b6b348c979f0034ed929dc95581.jpeg\" alt=\"Carlos-Sainz\">\n            </div>\n<div class=\"texto-contenido-derecha\">\n<h2>DESCUBRE TODOS LOS DETALLES DEL GRAN CIRCO</h2>\n<p>En <strong>Mundo F1</strong>, podrás encontrar toda la información, estadísticas y últimas noticias relacionadas con la máxima categoría de los deportes de motor. Aquí dispondrás de la información actualizada tras cada <strong>Gran Premio</strong> con todos los datos actualizados al minuto, sesión a sesión.</p>\n<p>Explora nuestro sitio y descubre una nueva manera de disfrutar de tu <strong>deporte favorito</strong>.</p>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"contenedor-tarjetas-columnas\">\n<div class=\"tarjeta-estilo\">\n<div class=\"tarjeta-imagen\">\n            <img src=\"https://cdn.avpasion.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/sigue-gp-bahrein-formula-1-web-02.jpg\" alt=\"live-timing\" class=\"foto-tarjeta\"/>\n          </div>\n<div class=\"tarjeta-contenido\">\n<h3>Live Timings</h3>\n<p>No hay sesiones en directo.</p>\n<p>            <a href=\"#\" class=\"tarjeta-boton\">Ver más</a>\n          </div>\n</p></div>\n<div class=\"tarjeta-estilo\">\n<div class=\"tarjeta-imagen\">\n            <img src=\"https://media.revistagq.com/photos/67e3e76c647fcc7e2803ca27/16:9/w_2560%2Cc_limit/2187699741\" alt=\"tsunoda-lawson\" class=\"foto-tarjeta\"/>\n          </div>\n<div class=\"tarjeta-contenido\">\n<h3>Últimas noticias</h3>\n<p>Yuki Tsunoda, a Red Bull: Liam Lawson pilotará el RB a partir de Suzuka.</p>\n<p>            <a href=\"#\" class=\"tarjeta-boton\">Ver más</a>\n          </div>\n</p></div>\n<div class=\"tarjeta-estilo\">\n<div class=\"tarjeta-imagen\">\n            <img src=\"https://s10.s3c.es/imag/_v0/5120x2794/b/8/3/BBPHDB.jpg\" alt=\"Japon\" class=\"foto-tarjeta\"/>\n          </div>\n<div class=\"tarjeta-contenido\">\n<h3>Próxima Carrera</h3>\n<p>Toda la información sobre el GP de Japón.</p>\n<p>            <a href=\"#\" class=\"tarjeta-boton\">Ver más</a>\n          </div>\n</p></div>\n<div class=\"tarjeta-estilo\">\n<div class=\"tarjeta-imagen\">\n              <img src=\"https://imgresizer.eurosport.com/unsafe/1200x0/filters:format(jpeg)/origin-imgresizer.eurosport.com/2025/02/28/image-90710e0d-1722-4256-9cad-488a339e1c9b-85-2560-1440.jpeg\" alt=\"sainz-alonso\" class=\"foto-tarjeta\"/>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"tarjeta-contenido\">\n<h3>Españoles</h3>\n<p>Últimas noticias sobre Fernando Alonso y Carlos Sainz.</p>\n<p>              <a href=\"#\" class=\"tarjeta-boton\">Ver más</a>\n            </div>\n</p></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"pie-de-pagina\">\n<div class=\"container-redes-sociales\">\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"redes-sociales\">Instagram</a><br />\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"redes-sociales\">Facebook</a><br />\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"redes-sociales\">X</a><br />\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"redes-sociales\">Tik Tok</a><br />\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"redes-sociales\">Contacto</a>\n        </div>\n<div class=\"texto-pie\">\n<p>Esta página ha sido realizada por Pedro de la Rúa Lima.</p>\n</p></div>\n</section>\n<p></body><br />\n</html></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Mundo F1', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-04-03 23:06:29', '2025-04-03 21:06:29', '', 9, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=111', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(113, 2, '2025-04-03 23:09:21', '2025-04-03 21:09:21', '<style>\n.body {\n    width: 100vw !important;\n    max-width: 100% !important;\n    margin: 0 !important;\n    padding: 0 !important;\n}\n.barra-superior,\n.cuerpo,\n.contenedor-imagen-texto,\n.contenedor-tarjetas-columnas,\n.pie-de-pagina {\n    width: 100% !important;\n    max-width: 100% !important;\n    margin-left: 0 !important;\n    margin-right: 0 !important;\n    padding-left: 0 !important;\n    padding-right: 0 !important;\n}\n.encabezado-superior {\n    width: 60% !important;\n}\n    :root \n    --color-primario: #ff0000;\n    --color-secundario: #292929;\n    --color-terciario: #ffffff;\n    --color-texto: #ffffff;\n    --color-texto-alt: #292929;\n}\nbody {\n    margin: 0;<br />\n    font-family: \'Exo 2\';<br />\n    background-image: url(\'https://png.pngtree.com/png-clipart/20240812/original/pngtree-pattern-lines-seamless-vector-png-image_15752243.png\');<br />\n    background-position: center;<br />\n    background-size: cover;<br />\n    background-attachment: fixed;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.barra-superior {<br />\n    position:;<br />\n    top: 0;<br />\n    left: 0;<br />\n    width: 100%;<br />\n    height: 100%;<br />\n    max-width: 100vw;<br />\n    padding: 10px 20px;<br />\n    box-sizing: border-box;<br />\n    justify-items: center;<br />\n    z-index: 1000;<br />\n    margin: 0;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.encabezado-superior {<br />\n    display: flex;<br />\n    justify-content: space-between;<br />\n    align-items: center;<br />\n    border-radius: 30px;<br />\n    width: 55%;<br />\n    padding: 4px;<br />\n    background-color: var(--color-primario);<br />\n    box-sizing: border-box;<br />\n    position: relative;<br />\n    box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.botones-izquierda {<br />\n    display: flex;<br />\n    font-size: 25px;<br />\n    gap: 10px;<br />\n    flex: 1;<br />\n    justify-content: right;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.botones-derecha {<br />\n    display: flex;<br />\n    font-size: 25px;<br />\n    gap: 10px;<br />\n    flex: 1;<br />\n    justify-content: left;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.boton-header {<br />\n    padding: 10px 20px;<br />\n    color: var(--color-texto);<br />\n    text-decoration: none;<br />\n    font-weight: 600;<br />\n    border-radius: 15px;<br />\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;<br />\n    white-space: nowrap;<br />\n    display: inline-block;<br />\n    background: none;<br />\n    border: none;<br />\n    cursor: pointer;<br />\n    font-family: inherit;<br />\n    font-size: inherit;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.boton-header:hover {<br />\n    background-color: var(--color-texto);<br />\n    color: var(--color-texto-alt);<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.icono-boton img {<br />\n    height: 100px;<br />\n    width: auto;<br />\n    transition: transform 0.3s ease;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.icono-boton:hover img {<br />\n    transform: scale(1.1);<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.menu-desplegable {<br />\n    position: relative;<br />\n    display: inline-block;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.contenido-menus {<br />\n    display: none;<br />\n    position: absolute;<br />\n    background-color: var(--color-terciario);<br />\n    width: 100%;<br />\n    min-width: max-content;<br />\n    box-shadow: 0px 8px 16px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);<br />\n    z-index: 1;<br />\n    border-radius: 0 0 15px 15px;<br />\n    overflow: hidden;<br />\n    top: 100%;<br />\n    left: 0;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.contenido-menus a {<br />\n    color: var(--color-texto-alt);<br />\n    padding: 12px 16px;<br />\n    text-decoration: none;<br />\n    display: block;<br />\n    font-size: 18px;<br />\n    transition: background-color 0.3s;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.contenido-menus a:hover {<br />\n    background-color: #f1f1f1;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.menu-desplegable:hover .contenido-menus {<br />\n    display: block;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.menu-desplegable > .boton-header {<br />\n    width: 100%;<br />\n    box-sizing: border-box;<br />\n    text-align: center;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.menu-desplegable:hover .boton-header {<br />\n    background-color: var(--color-texto);<br />\n    color: var(--color-primario);<br />\n    border-radius: 15px 15px 0 0;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.cuerpo {<br />\n    margin-top: 50px;<br />\n    height: 40vh;<br />\n    background-image: url(\'https://www.formula1.com/content/dam/fom-website/manual/Misc/2022manual/WinterFebruary/GettyImages-1235524583.jpg\');<br />\n    background-position-x: center;<br />\n    background-position-y: -60vh;<br />\n    background-size: cover;<br />\n    height: 300px;<br />\n    display: flex;<br />\n    align-items: center;<br />\n    justify-content: center;<br />\n    position: relative;<br />\n    box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.cuerpo::before {<br />\n    content: \'\';<br />\n    position: absolute;<br />\n    top: 0;<br />\n    left: 0;<br />\n    right: 0;<br />\n    bottom: 0;<br />\n    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.contenido-cuerpo {<br />\n    position: relative;<br />\n    color: var(--color-texto);<br />\n    text-align: center;<br />\n    padding: 0 20px;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.contenido-cuerpo h1 {<br />\n    font-size: 90px;<br />\n    margin: 0;<br />\n    text-shadow: 5px 5px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.contenedor-imagen-texto {<br />\n    display: grid;<br />\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;<br />\n    align-items: start;<br />\n    max-width: 1200px;<br />\n    margin: 40px auto;<br />\n    gap: 40px;<br />\n    padding: 25px 50px;<br />\n    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-terciario), #e7e7e7, var(--color-terciario));<br />\n    border-radius: 50px;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.imagen-izquierda {<br />\n    position: relative;<br />\n    overflow: hidden;<br />\n    border-radius: 50px;<br />\n    height: auto;<br />\n    max-height: 400px;<br />\n    aspect-ratio: 16/18;<br />\n    display: flex;<br />\n    align-items: center;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.imagen-izquierda img {<br />\n    width: 100%;<br />\n    height: auto;<br />\n    object-fit: contain;<br />\n    transition: transform 0.5s ease;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.texto-contenido-derecha {<br />\n    display: flex;<br />\n    flex-direction: column;<br />\n    justify-content: center;<br />\n    height: 100%;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.texto-contenido-derecha h2 {<br />\n    color: #ff0000;<br />\n    font-size: 40px;<br />\n    text-align: left;<br />\n    text-justify: auto;<br />\n    margin-bottom: 15px;<br />\n    line-height: 1.3;<br />\n    position: relative;<br />\n    padding-bottom: 12px;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.texto-contenido-derecha p {<br />\n    font-size: 16px;<br />\n    line-height: 1.3;<br />\n    color: #292929;<br />\n    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;<br />\n}<br />\n.contenedor-tarjetas-columnas {<br />\n    display: grid;<br />\n    justify-content: center;<br />\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 300px);<br />\n    gap: 75px;<br />\n    margin: 50px 0;<br />\n    padding-top: 50px;<br />\n    width: 100%;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.tarjeta-estilo {<br />\n    background: var(--color-primario);<br />\n    border-radius: 30px;<br />\n    overflow: hidden;<br />\n    box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);<br />\n    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;<br />\n    display: flex;<br />\n    flex-direction: column;<br />\n    height: 100%;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.tarjeta-estilo:hover {<br />\n    transform: translateY(-10px);<br />\n    box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.tarjeta-imagen {<br />\n    height: 250px;<br />\n    overflow: hidden;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.tarjeta-imagen img {<br />\n    width: 100%;<br />\n    height: 100%;<br />\n    object-fit: cover;<br />\n    transition: transform 0.5s ease;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.tarjeta-estilo:hover .tarjeta-imagen img {<br />\n    transform: scale(1.05);<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.tarjeta-contenido {<br />\n    padding: 20px 20px;<br />\n    flex-grow: 1;<br />\n    display: flex;<br />\n    flex-direction: column;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.tarjeta-contenido h3 {<br />\n    font-family: \'Exo 2\';<br />\n    text-align: center;<br />\n    font-size: 30px;<br />\n    letter-spacing: 0.5px;<br />\n    margin-bottom: 20px;<br />\n    color: var(--color-texto);<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.tarjeta-contenido p {<br />\n    font-family: \'Exo 2\';<br />\n    text-align: center;<br />\n    font-size: 15px;<br />\n    color: var(--color-texto);<br />\n    margin-bottom: 20px;<br />\n    line-height: 1.6;<br />\n    flex-grow: 1;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.tarjeta-boton {<br />\n    display: inline-block;<br />\n    padding: 12px 25px;<br />\n    background: var(--color-terciario);<br />\n    color: var(--color-primario);<br />\n    text-decoration: none;<br />\n    border-radius: 30px;<br />\n    font-family: \'Exo 2\';<br />\n    font-size: 1.2rem;<br />\n    font-weight: 600;<br />\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;<br />\n    text-align: center;<br />\n    margin-top: auto;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.tarjeta-boton:hover {<br />\n    transform: translateY(10px);<br />\n    background: var(--color-secundario);<br />\n    color: var(--color-texto);<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.pie-de-pagina {<br />\n    display: flex;<br />\n    flex-direction: column;<br />\n    align-items: center;<br />\n    justify-content: center;<br />\n    padding: 20px 0px;<br />\n    margin-top: 250px;<br />\n    margin-bottom: 0;<br />\n    background: linear-gradient(0deg, var(--color-secundario)25%, #303030, var(--color-secundario)75%);<br />\n    height: 300px;<br />\n    min-height: 100%;<br />\n    width: 100%;<br />\n    max-width: 100vw;<br />\n    border-radius:0px;<br />\n    box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.container-redes-sociales {<br />\n    display: flex;<br />\n    justify-content: center;<br />\n    gap: 20px;<br />\n    width: 80%;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.redes-sociales {<br />\n    padding: 12px 24px;<br />\n    color: var(--color-texto);<br />\n    text-decoration: none;<br />\n    font-weight: 600;<br />\n    border-radius: 30px;<br />\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;<br />\n    white-space: nowrap;<br />\n    background: none;<br />\n    cursor: pointer;<br />\n    font-family: \'Exo 2\';<br />\n    font-size: 1.2rem;<br />\n    margin: 0;<br />\n    display: inline-flex;<br />\n    align-items: center;<br />\n    justify-content: center;<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.redes-sociales:hover {<br />\n    background-color: var(--color-texto);<br />\n    color: var(--color-primario);<br />\n    transform: translateY(-3px);<br />\n}</p>\n<p>.texto-pie {<br />\n    padding-top: 200px;<br />\n    font-family: \'Exo 2\';<br />\n    font-size: 12px;<br />\n    color: var(--color-texto);<br />\n}<br />\n</style>\n<p><!DOCTYPE html><br />\n<html lang=\"es\"><br />\n<head><br />\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><br />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><br />\n    <title>Mundo F1</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"HeaderConBotonesCSS.css\">\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Exo+2:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n</head><br />\n<body></p>\n<section class=\"barra-superior\">\n<div class=\"encabezado-superior\">\n<div class=\"botones-izquierda\">\n<div class=\"menu-desplegable\">\n                    <button class=\"boton-header\">PILOTOS</button></p>\n<div class=\"contenido-menus\">\n                        <a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/2025/04/03/max-verstappen/\">Verstappen</a><br />\n                        <a href=\"#\">Tsunoda</a><br />\n                        <a href=\"#\">Norris</a><br />\n                        <a href=\"#\">Piastri</a><br />\n                        <a href=\"#\">Leclerc</a><br />\n                        <a href=\"#\">Hamilton</a><br />\n                        <a href=\"#\">Russell</a><br />\n                        <a href=\"#\">Antonneli</a><br />\n                        <a href=\"#\">Alonso</a><br />\n                        <a href=\"#\">Stroll</a><br />\n                  