(127, 2, '2025-04-04 00:31:06', '2025-04-03 22:31:06', '<!-- wp:group {\"tagName\":\"main\",\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\"},\"padding\":{\"top\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"default\"}} -->\n<main class=\"wp-block-group alignfull\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;min-height:100vh\">\n    <!-- wp:post-content {\"align\":\"full\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"default\",\"contentSize\":\"100%\",\"wideSize\":\"100%\"},\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\"}}} /-->\n</main>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<style>\n    /* CSS adicional para asegurar el 100% de altura */\n    html, body {\n        margin: 0 !important;\n        padding: 0 !important;\n        height: 100% !important;\n    }\n    \n    .wp-block-group.alignfull {\n        width: 100vw !important;\n        max-width: 100% !important;\n        margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%) !important;\n    }\n    \n    main.wp-block-group {\n        display: flex !important;\n        flex-direction: column !important;\n    }\n    \n    .wp-block-post-content {\n        flex-grow: 1 !important;\n        width: 100% !important;\n        max-width: 100% !important;\n        padding-left: 0 !important;\n        padding-right: 0 !important;\n    }\n</style>', 'Entradas individuales', 'Muestra una entrada individual en tu web, a menos que se le haya aplicado una plantilla personalizada o exista una plantilla dedicada.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '123-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-04-04 00:31:06', '2025-04-03 22:31:06', '', 123, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=127', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
